        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Protection of Social Security Benefits Restoration Act&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;This bill prohibits the application of, and repeals authority for, administrative offsets to Social Security, railroad retirement, and black lung benefits. (An administrative offset is the withholding of funds payable by or held by the United States to satisfy a debt.)&lt;/p&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
      </summary>
